==German==
===Noun===
'''Sozialparasit''' ''m'' (''pl'' Sozialparasiten)
# (Biology): literally, "social [[parasite]]", a parasite of social animals utilizing common resources; e.g. [[wasp]]s that live in [[beehive]]s or [[bumblebee]] nests, feeding on [[honey]] or [[larvae]].
# (derogatory): [[welfare parasite]]

